Title: With love from Nepal
DateModified: '2019-03-02'
DatePublished: '2019-03-02'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/with-love-from-nepal
SetInCountry: Nepal
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Ashutosh Chauhan
AuthorCountry: India
Text: I reached the Nepal by 1pm in the noon and I took taxi to the hotel which is
  located in front of pashupatinath temple the view of hotel is good me and my friend
  walk around the street and in the evening we went to thamel street which is about
  6km away from the hotel and we took taxi as you know when your in other countries
  the price were over rated we reached the street we heard something about the street
  that there are prostitute are easily available but when we walked around the street
  the things were normal and we don't found anything like that.
